理，實情就可能只有圍牆隔開其他村屋，就話自己係屋苑式管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"下咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以真係諗緊買唔買村屋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"真係自己去睇下個屋苑先，我見新起嗰啲大部份都係假屋苑式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但舊嗰啲真屋苑式，我諗30年樓齡以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad77ddce8920a1f45ddcdb878b5626da4075e4a7","tid":1947283,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:28:01.000Z","msg":"鄉黑套丁屋"},{"pid":"c33d8396d11721a73bdd619d7b86f5a89a62ef8b","tid":1947283,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"如果樓豬灣仔翻工嘅話<br />\n元朗加州花園都幾好嘅<br />\n佢哋有shuttle bus出港島 上水 同元朗<br />\n買屋就有兩個車位 <br />\n同埋又有會所 <br />\n唔嫌佢隔涉嘅話都幾好"},{"pid":"7cf857c6157e6acd30477757ed783cefda36775a","tid":1947283,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91baaf234ca828b53fc0b4e213136ceabfcfcdd0","tid":1947283,"uid":6875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T00:15:13.000Z","msg":"有幾多有管理村屋有光纖？<br />\n我諗呢個都好重要<br />\n3m 網上行/4g卡 不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"屋企好似用緊100mb"},{"pid":"1e5c90c4aaab5449aebea7d1a71b318de28a6257","tid":1947283,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c33d8396d11721a73bdd619d7b86f5a89a62ef8b","tid":1947283,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"如果樓豬灣仔翻工嘅話<br />\n元朗加州花園都幾好嘅<br />\n佢哋有shuttle bus出港島 上水 同元朗<br />\n買屋就有兩個車位 <br />\n同埋又有會所 <br />\n唔嫌佢隔涉嘅話都幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"加洲花園唔算隔涉啦，揸車經大欖隧道行西隧出中環都只係大概六七個字就到。"},{"pid":"9fb2f61285c9e38c40bbd3d78d281f1740310eb3","tid":1947283,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7