0e87673","tid":1947283,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:39:54.000Z","msg":"如果想租 大西北村屋 連車位<br />\n用咩途徑去搵好？<br />\n網上Apps 定 現場地產鋪 定其他？"},{"pid":"3b78df170d776b11bd2cf864b1acc2d654c90f7d","tid":1947283,"uid":51105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c33d8396d11721a73bdd619d7b86f5a89a62ef8b","tid":1947283,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T01:43:03.000Z","msg":"如果樓豬灣仔翻工嘅話<br />\n元朗加州花園都幾好嘅<br />\n佢哋有shuttle bus出港島 上水 同元朗<br />\n買屋就有兩個車位 <br />\n同埋又有會所 <br />\n唔嫌佢隔涉嘅話都幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:53:58.000Z","msg":"呢啲應該係叫獨立屋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗啲人話買村屋，唔會諗錦繡，加州同康樂園掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c71a84fc34bad83907701067e1a89e937fd85ec2","tid":1947283,"uid":258999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"自己去果d屋苑睇一睇，有管理公司既門口會有保安同有公司名果d野，唔好懶。<br />\n<br />\n不過其實有管理公司只係好少少，叫塞屎渠揾到人幫手咁，因為呢d村都係d原居民套丁起出黎，最後話事權都係d原居民到，外人入去住有事都係食屎。"},{"pid":"bb1bf93f9f865e12e887623a15dfe3557a5c288d","tid":1947283,"uid":66908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SS07AhK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSS07AhK.png&h=3045f03d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可以去呢邊睇下先，錦田河，錦泰路呢邊其實幾好住，可以踩單車到南生圍，元朗<br />\n之前踩單車都見到一啲屋苑式幾靚<br />\n我自己就住橫台山個邊"},{"pid":"c82ea6739141644cceb0e137047a694459e1dce1","tid":1947283,"uid":50660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85899b38fd13a50588f8831896a985159c4377bd","tid":1947283,"uid":27067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43e3eec2e7c6e5d6193537f3be67f91e00733528","tid":1947283,"uid":75256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"500966c97d788122